commit.message: Documented the Tox handshake/AKE in docs/tox_handshake.md and added comments regarding the handshake/AKE in net_crypto.c.
Executed astyle/format-source for Travis to pass.
Added comment/TODO in tox_handshake.md and a few new comments in net_crypto.
Add a few minor comments.
Added a few comments regarding the handshake.
Starting adding Noise stuff to toxcore.
Changed CMakeLists.txt to include noise-c during build. Started implementing the noise handshake in Tox and added additional comments regarding the current Tox handshake for better understanding.
Continued implementing Noise handshake. Added first handshake message to create_crypto_handshake() function. Added comments regarding the existing and new handshake.
Continued working on handle_crypto_handshake(), Problem is that the peer doesn't know the static public key of the other in handle_new_connection_handshake().
Added debug output and fixed 2 minior bugs.
When receiving a handshake packet, check if it's the correct Noise action.
Implemented initialize_handshake(), create_crypto_handshake() and handle_crypto_handshake() based on IK pattern/different handshake packets from Initiator and Responder.
Changed/added some comments.
Fixed bug in initialize_handshake().
Fixed wrong role - RESPONDER instead of INITIATOR - in initialize_handshake().
Hopefully fixed length bug in message buffer / handshake packet length.
Implemented handshake start on RESPONDER side.
Implemented handling of handshake packets in handle_packet_connection() and accept_crypto_connection().
Implemented Noise handshakestate split for send+recv cipher.
Using Noise sending and receiving cipher for encryption/decryption instead of old shared_key.
Implemented packet encryption and decryption using Noise and NoiseCipherStates.
Removed base nonce from implementation because it's not needed (Noise ChaCha20 instead of XSalsa20). Also removed not-needed variables from Crypto_connection and New_connection structs.
Improved comments, added some info and small code changes.
Implemented wipeing crypto connection if handshake fails.
Fixed connection wipe, wipe_crypto_connection() was not available everywhere I used it.
Fixed double free/segfault bug when calling noise_handshakestate_free() twice.
Run astyle on net_crypto.c.
